'''碳龟属'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Carbonemys''）是一属已灭绝的[[侧颈龟亚目|侧颈龟类]]，于哥伦比亚东北部Cesar-Ranchería盆地的距今约6000万到5700万年前的古新世中期[[塞雷洪组|塞雷洪组]]地层中被发现，其出现年代大约始于[[白垩纪﹣古近纪灭绝事件|白垩纪﹣古近纪灭绝事件]]后500万年。<ref name="Carbonemys">{{Cite journal | last1 = [[Edwin_Cadena|Cadena]] | first1 = E. A. | last2 = Ksepka | first2 = D. T. | last3 = Jaramillo | first3 = C. A. | last4 = Bloch | first4 = J. I. | title = New pelomedusoid turtles from the late Palaeocene Cerrejón Formation of Colombia and their implications for phylogeny and body size evolution | doi = 10.1080/14772019.2011.569031 | journal = Journal of Systematic Palaeontology | volume = 10 | issue = 2 | pages = 313 | year = 2012 | pmid = | pmc = }}</ref>

==发现==
2005年，北卡罗莱纳州立大学一位名叫埃德温·卡德纳的博士生在Cerrejón煤矿发现了碳龟属的[[正模标本|正模标本]]。它的壳长约1.72米（5英尺8英寸），是世界上最大的[[乌龟|乌龟]]之一。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://phys.org/news/2012-05-reveal-ancient-giant-turtle-fossil.html| title = Researchers reveal ancient giant turtle fossil| date = 17 May 2012| publisher = Phys.Org| access-date = 18 May 2012| archive-date = 2012-09-22| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6ArUDvcn6?url=http://phys.org/news/2012-05-reveal-ancient-giant-turtle-fossil.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Maugh II|first=Thomas H.|title=Researchers find fossil of a turtle that was size of a Smart car|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/science/sciencenow/la-sci-sn-largest-turtle-20120518,0,6876731.story|work=LA Times|access-date=18 May 2012|date=18 May 2012|archive-date=2012-09-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ArUEZZxJ?url=http://www.latimes.com/news/science/sciencenow/la-sci-sn-largest-turtle-20120518,0,6876731.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>

碳龟属的下颚很巨大，足以吃掉鳄鱼，这些鳄鱼在Cerrejón组最初的新热带森林中数量非常丰富。这类乌龟还与巨大的[[泰坦巨蟒属|泰坦巨蟒属]]共存过。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.discovery.com/animals/car-sized-turtle-found-in-colombian-coal-mine.html |title=Car-sized Turtle Found in Colombian Coal Mine : Discovery News |publisher=News.discovery.com |date=2012-05-18 |access-date=2012-06-14 |archive-date=2012-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121123182945/http://news.discovery.com/animals/car-sized-turtle-found-in-colombian-coal-mine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

